<br>
Parry is usefull but you can't use BwT until about level 45 and it will probably be nerfed by then.  Riposte is marginally usefully also, but a low priority. <br>
<br>
Max all of your abilities, Martial arts &amp; Brawl every level for sure.  Focus your IPs spent on Nano skills to get Dirty fighter, and then raise time &amp; space to get Subconscious guiding. <br>
<br>
MA weapons: They use Melee init.  I have 5 of these weapons now and they all suck.  If you find one that use can use without spending IP then go ahead, but the effect will be minimal.<br>
<br>
&quot;Give&quot; nanos:  these are very low priority nanos.  Don't spend IP to get them.<br>
